author: Greg Rajan, Matt Young, Houston Chronicle
title: Best NFL memes from Week 6
text:
Best NFL memes from Week 6 1 / 25 Back to Gallery 
The once-mighty Seattle Seahawks dropped to 2-4 and the Indianapolis Colts tried to trick the tricky New England Patriots with an absolutely awful fake punt. 
The Internet's meme artists had fun with both of those NFL Sunday happenings and every other fan base that has fallen on hard times. These memes are good enough that even fans of losing teams have to laugh. 
Click through the gallery above to check out some of the best memes from week 6 in the NFL.
